      <title>WeWork 创始人诺依曼希望破产法院帮助其回购公司</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/wework-founder-neumann-wants-bankruptcy-courts-help-bid-repurchase-company-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[WeWork 创始人 Adam Neumann 已请求美国破产法官帮助他重新收购联合办公业务，并于周一表示 WeWork 管理层应该进行谈判，否则将被迫放弃对公司重组的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/wework-founder-neumann-wants-bankruptcy-courts-help-bid-repurchase-company-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 19:52:39 GMT</pubDate>
